data.description: Experience modern living in this beautiful home built by CDW Construction. Situated on a corner lot in Skycrest Subdivision, this home offers a comfortable and elegant space to call home. A wide entry opens to a stunning kitchen, dining and living area with high tray ceilings, modern lighting, large windows & gas FP. Kitchen features quartz countertops, gas stove, sleek stainless appliances & an island perfect for entertaining. Laundry, 3 beds, 2 baths, a separate office~all on the main level. Primary bedroom suite boasts tray ceiling, double sinks, quartz, spacious tiled shower & walk-in closet. Additional highlights include oversized 3 car garage w/workbench, RV parking w/dump station, covered back patio w/ privacy screens, ample storage & a partially finished daylight basement designed for 2 beds, bathroom, and large family room. Live comfortably & create your dream space downstairs!
